					<p>
						<b>Communication & Constituent Services</b>
					</p>
					<p>
						Communication is a vital component to any successful organization and Tim has made it a cornerstone of his term in office. In order to be effective, your representative must be in tune with the issues and concerns facing the 4th Ward.
					</p>
					<br>				
					<p>
						Tim is the most active member of the city council, meeting with constituents daily, hearing their concerns, and taking action.
					</p>
					<br>
					<p>
						Tim’s monthly newsletter to 4th ward residents keeps them apprised of issues pertaining to the ward and the city. These newsletters serve as a status report on current legislation and how it affects residents. Tim has also used this database of residents to warn the 4th Ward of emergency events occurring in the city, including flooding, major traffic alerts, and any potential health related warnings. To receive the newsletters just sign up on the home page.
					</p>
					<br>
					<p>
						Tim has made it a priority to attend Hoboken Housing Authority meetings as a member of the public. He has also been meeting with small groups as requested.
					</p>
					<br>
					<p>
						Tim believes in being an independent voice for the 4th Ward and the only way to make that happen is with an open and direct line of communication between residents and thjeir elected 4th Ward Councilman.
					</p>
					<br>
					<p>
						Tim doesn’t believe that any one party has all the answers when it comes to doing what’s in the best interest of the 4th Ward. Everyone deserves to have their views heard, and Tim will fight to make sure residents have a representative who refuses to be pulled into the partisan politics that have plagued Hoboken for so many years. Collapse…
					</p>
					<br>
					<p>
						<b>Commitment</b>
					</p>
					<p>
						Tim believes in a commitment to excellence in all aspects of his life: personal, professional, or public. Taking pride in his work, no matter how big or small the task is before him, Tim always puts forth 100% effort. There are many challenges facing the 4th Ward that will take several years to accomplish and Tim will see these challenges through to completion.
					</p>
					<br>
					<p>						
						<b>Business Development</b>
					</p>
					<p>
						Tim Occhipinti supports all business owners in Hoboken. Small businesses, in particular, play a vital role in the economic growth and development in our neighborhoods. They are the lifeblood of our community, providing jobs, food, retail goods and key services that support the daily lives of residents in the 4th Ward.		
					</p>
